Password Reset Request
======================

You are receiving this email because a request was made to reset the password for your Pasabaya account.

You can reset your password by copying and pasting the link below into your browser:

<%= edit_password_url(@user.password_reset_token) %>

⏳ EXPIRATION NOTICE
--------------------
For security reasons, this password reset link will expire in <%= distance_of_time_in_words(0, @user.password_reset_token_expires_in) %>. After that, you will need to request a new link.

🛡️ DIDN'T REQUEST THIS?
-----------------------
If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged and your account secure.

